WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.700
Ah, what’s happening?

2
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:09.066
I must have been out of my mind.

3
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:10.900
I should have pushed him away immediately.

4
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.066
Your Majesty.

5
00:00:15.066 --> 00:00:15.866
Ah.

6
00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:20.000
From now on, all matters of the harem will be decided by you.

7
00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:21.000
What?

8
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:24.466
Your Majesty, isn’t this against propriety?

9
00:00:24.466 --> 00:00:27.066
The harem already has the Empress Dowager and Consort Yan.

10
00:00:27.066 --> 00:00:28.966
I am merely a new consort.

11
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.700
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

12
00:00:30.866 --> 00:00:31.900
It’s only a matter of time.

13
00:00:32.166 --> 00:00:35.200
So it’s settled. I will speak to the Empress Dowager about this.

14
00:00:35.566 --> 00:00:36.766
As for Consort Yan,

15
00:00:37.333 --> 00:00:38.400
don’t worry about her.

16
00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:41.066
It’s only a matter of time.

17
00:00:41.066 --> 00:00:41.966
What do you mean?

18
00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:44.166
The Emperor no longer favors Consort Yan.

19
00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:46.433
They must have really had a fight.

20
00:00:46.466 --> 00:00:47.900
I still have state affairs to attend to.

21
00:00:47.900 --> 00:00:49.000
Rest well.

22
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.266
I’ll come back to see you later.

23
00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:56.300
I’m most familiar with handling state affairs.

24
00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.500
But the Emperor’s attitude

25
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.400
is really hard to figure out.

26
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:04.000
Chief Steward Li, Consort Rong is strong-willed.

27
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.133
Stay and assist her.

28
00:01:05.133 --> 00:01:07.300
If there are any troubles you can’t resolve, come to me.

29
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:08.100
Yes.

30
00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:11.966
The world of the harem,

31
00:01:11.966 --> 00:01:14.100
is about to change.

32
00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:16.800
Hahahahahaha.

33
00:01:20.133 --> 00:01:24.366
Consort, handle all the grievances of the minor consorts.

34
00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:27.433
Next month is the Empress Dowager’s birthday banquet.

35
00:01:27.466 --> 00:01:29.033
You can start preparing early.

36
00:01:35.066 --> 00:01:36.233
One month later.

37
00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:38.700
Go.

38
00:01:40.100 --> 00:01:41.766
To Cuixin Lake.
